; boop.ap: demonstrates the LCC+ `boop` trap.
; `bop` is the LCC+ sound alias; `boop` was retired in favor of five configured
; sound slots. This demo uses `bop`, which aliases to `sound 2`.
; Run:  node src/plus/lccplus.js plusdemos/boop.ap
        .lccplus
        lea r0, msg
        sout r0
        nl
        bop             ; alias for sound 2
        halt
msg:    .string "boop.ap: playing the bop sound slot..."
